comments: She LOVES the 18th Century and in shows. She is very knowledgeable and helpful. Be ready to read and write a lot. This class is writing intensive even if it doesn\'t say so. You will have 7 reaction papers, 1 long paper, quizzes, and a group presentation (even in online classes). It\'s a lot of work, but the class is not hard.

tag_professor: Gives good feedback (2)  Get ready to read (2)  Participation matters (2)
comments: LOVE this class. Her classes were mostly discussion, and no tests. It is reading and writing intensive but she loves to help. She makes class interesting and you can tell she is interested in what she does. She doesn\'t shoot any ideas down as long as you can support it. I would recommend this class x100 if you have any interest in English <33
